Package BobcatLib.Hardware.Controllers

Class OI

java.lang.Object
BobcatLib.Hardware.Controllers.OI
public class OI extends Object
The Operator Interface (OI) class manages the controller inputs and button mappings for the robot's driver. It supports various controller types and their configurations.
